@* localhost:5000/vendors/{id}/orders/{id} *@
@* Page to show all orders from a particular vendor *@
@* Routed from "/vendors", this page will look like "/vendors/{id}/orders" and will also contain a link to make a new order "/vendors/{id}/orders/new" *@
@* Should contain buttons to go to new order, back to vendor list, or home *@

<h1>Order Details</h1>


<p>Order name: @Model["orders"].Contents</p>
<p>Description: @Model["orders"].OrderDescription</p>
<p>Date placed: @Model["orders"].OrderDate</p>
<p>Price: $@Model["orders"].OrderPrice</p>

<p><a href='/vendors/@Model["vendors"].Id/'>Back</a> to all orders for @Model["vendors"].Name.</p>
